data.description: Beautifully newly remodeled 3 bedroom/2 bath house nestled among the oak trees of Perdido Bay Oaks.  Roof- 2021, 2022- heat pump, duct cleaning, luxury vinyl plank flooring, granite and onyx counter tops, new plumbing and complete kitchen and bathroom remodel.  The bathroom remodels are showcased with beautiful onyx in the bathroom showers and on the bathroom countertops.The kitchen has a butler's pantry along with another pantry (plenty of storage) and under the counter lighting.  This house has been remodeled to be a bran new home.  No stops were held.  Only the best moulding, hardware, flooring, counters and lighting!  The property includes water access with a dock that stretches over Perdido Bay.  .  The screened in back porch is a lovely place to listen to the birds in the trees and relax.  There are plumb and orange trees in the yard along with a huge magnolia tree.  1 mile from the Lillian boat launch.  20 minutes to all the conveniences of Foley, Alabama and Pensacola, Fl.  20 min to the luxurious white sand beaches of Gulf Shores and Perdido Key.  Nearest grocery store is 5 miles.  All measurements and facts are thought to be correct, but to be deemed correct by buyers or buyer's agent.  Come view this gem of a property.
